  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/5147a5cfdc9f40273a4187d573c253a6.poster.avif?t=1738530161\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/5147a5cfdc9f40273a4187d573c253a6.webm?t=1738530161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/5147a5cfdc9f40273a4187d573c253a6.mp4?t=1738530161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/bbd398a80021f1eb975e606c604da838.avif?t=1738530161\" width=450 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Food Delivery Simulator\" is an immersive game where you take the role of being a food delivery driver. Explore the city, upgrade your ride, and become a top-rated driver!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/45011768b6454e2a9d417d67ed8a2899.avif?t=1738530161\" width=800 height=100 /></span>You get to decide when you want to start working and which deliveries to accept. Make sure you maximize your delivery rates by having a higher rating and better equipment to make sure your food arrives in style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/c49716f1b7a2b18eb71dc895b71970c5.poster.avif?t=1738530161\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/c49716f1b7a2b18eb71dc895b71970c5.webm?t=1738530161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/c49716f1b7a2b18eb71dc895b71970c5.mp4?t=1738530161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/1e33fa95cd2ed1d72cec39579dce74cc.avif?t=1738530161\" width=800 height=100 /></span>Working as a food delivery driver is no easy job! Make sure you arrive on time and avoid a bumpy ride, the quality of your delivery will affect your rating from the customers. Some may get angry and throw the food in your face!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/f581652d99d6b491acac9ab532e2be4f.poster.avif?t=1738530161\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/f581652d99d6b491acac9ab532e2be4f.webm?t=1738530161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/f581652d99d6b491acac9ab532e2be4f.mp4?t=1738530161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/2d83fb0c47a667f7e1c11879dc08e8de.avif?t=1738530161\" width=800 height=100 /></span>Use your computer at home or your phone to check e-mails, pay your bills, and browse the market for new equipment. Fun mini-games are also hidden within the devices!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/73cb59da025a02df79725ba10799020c.poster.avif?t=1738530161\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/73cb59da025a02df79725ba10799020c.webm?t=1738530161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/73cb59da025a02df79725ba10799020c.mp4?t=1738530161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/13bf0ecb7591b40a59ddcb3bdee5d4de.avif?t=1738530161\" width=800 height=100 /></span>Make use of the market app to purchase or rent better bikes that are faster and more stable to make your deliveries smoother. Insulated bags can also be upgraded in the market (Coming soon)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/5f12adcb8db74fed12e5f83a4575c59e.poster.avif?t=1738530161\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/5f12adcb8db74fed12e5f83a4575c59e.webm?t=1738530161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/5f12adcb8db74fed12e5f83a4575c59e.mp4?t=1738530161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/fac52f9b71bfac31221c4d706c828649.avif?t=1738530161\" width=800 height=100 /></span>Tired of delivering? You may visit the club at night to have some fun and try your chance at getting a girlfriend. You can also play fun classic games such as BJ and Exotic Squad on your computer at home.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/5147a5cfdc9f40273a4187d573c253a6.poster.avif?t=1738530161\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/5147a5cfdc9f40273a4187d573c253a6.webm?t=1738530161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/5147a5cfdc9f40273a4187d573c253a6.mp4?t=1738530161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/bbd398a80021f1eb975e606c604da838.avif?t=1738530161\" width=450 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Food Delivery Simulator\" is an immersive game where you take the role of being a food delivery driver. Explore the city, upgrade your ride, and become a top-rated driver!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/45011768b6454e2a9d417d67ed8a2899.avif?t=1738530161\" width=800 height=100 /></span>You get to decide when you want to start working and which deliveries to accept. Make sure you maximize your delivery rates by having a higher rating and better equipment to make sure your food arrives in style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/c49716f1b7a2b18eb71dc895b71970c5.poster.avif?t=1738530161\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986370/extras/c49716f1b7a2b18eb71dc895b71970c5.webm?t=1738530161\" type=\"video